{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Do you ever feel completely overwhelmed"},{"time":2000,"text":"when you're faced with a complex problem?"},{"time":5000,"text":"Well, I hope to change that in less than three minutes."},{"time":8000,"text":"So, I hope to convince you that complex"},{"time":10000,"text":"doesn't always equal complicated."},{"time":12000,"text":"So for me, a well-crafted baguette, fresh out of the oven,"},{"time":15000,"text":"is complex,"},{"time":17000,"text":"but a curry onion green olive poppy cheese bread"},{"time":19000,"text":"is complicated."},{"time":22000,"text":"I'm an ecologist, and I study complexity. I love complexity."},{"time":25000,"text":"And I study that in the natural world, the interconnectedness of species."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"So here's a food web,"},{"time":30000,"text":"or a map of feeding links between species"},{"time":32000,"text":"that live in Alpine Lakes in the mountains of California."},{"time":35000,"text":"And this is what happens to that food web"},{"time":37000,"text":"when it's stocked with non-native fish that never lived there before."},{"time":39000,"text":"All the grayed-out species disappear."},{"time":41000,"text":"Some are actually on the brink of extinction."},{"time":43000,"text":"And lakes with fish have more mosquitos, even though they eat them."},{"time":46000,"text":"These effects were all unanticipated,"},{"time":48000,"text":"and yet we're discovering they're predictable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"So I want to share with you a couple key insights"},{"time":52000,"text":"about complexity we're learning from studying nature"},{"time":54000,"text":"that maybe are applicable to other problems."},{"time":58000,"text":"First is the simple power of good visualization tools"},{"time":60000,"text":"to help untangle complexity"},{"time":62000,"text":"and just encourage you to ask questions you didn't think of before."},{"time":65000,"text":"For example, you could plot the flow of carbon"},{"time":68000,"text":"through corporate supply chains in a corporate ecosystem,"},{"time":71000,"text":"or the interconnections of habitat patches"},{"time":73000,"text":"for endangered species in Yosemite National Park."},{"time":76000,"text":"The next thing is that if you want to predict"},{"time":78000,"text":"the effect of one species on another,"},{"time":80000,"text":"if you focus only on that link,"},{"time":82000,"text":"and then you black box the rest,"},{"time":84000,"text":"it's actually less predictable"},{"time":86000,"text":"than if you step back, consider the entire system -- all the species, all the links --"},{"time":89000,"text":"and from that place,"},{"time":91000,"text":"hone in on the sphere of influence that matters most."},{"time":93000,"text":"And we're discovering, with our research,"},{"time":95000,"text":"that's often very local to the node you care about"},{"time":97000,"text":"within one or two degrees."},{"time":99000,"text":"So the more you step back, embrace complexity,"},{"time":101000,"text":"the better chance you have of finding simple answers,"},{"time":103000,"text":"and it's often different than the simple answer that you started with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"So let's switch gears and look at a really complex problem"},{"time":110000,"text":"courtesy of the U.S. government."},{"time":113000,"text":"This is a diagram of the U.S. counterinsurgency strategy in Afghanistan."},{"time":116000,"text":"It was front page of the New York Times a couple months ago."},{"time":119000,"text":"Instantly ridiculed by the media"},{"time":121000,"text":"for being so crazy complicated."},{"time":123000,"text":"And the stated goal was to increase popular support"},{"time":125000,"text":"for the Afghan government."},{"time":127000,"text":"Clearly a complex problem,"},{"time":129000,"text":"but is it complicated?"},{"time":131000,"text":"Well, when I saw this in the front page of the Times,"},{"time":133000,"text":"I thought, \"Great. Finally something I can relate to."},{"time":135000,"text":"I can sink my teeth into this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"So let's do it. So here we go for the first time ever,"},{"time":140000,"text":"a world premiere view of this spaghetti diagram as an ordered network."},{"time":143000,"text":"The circled node is the one we're trying to influence --"},{"time":145000,"text":"popular support for the government."},{"time":147000,"text":"And so now we can look one degrees, two degrees,"},{"time":149000,"text":"three degrees away from that node"},{"time":151000,"text":"and eliminate three-quarters of the diagram outside that sphere of influence."},{"time":154000,"text":"Within that sphere,"},{"time":156000,"text":"most of those nodes are not actionable, like the harshness of the terrain,"},{"time":159000,"text":"and a very small minority are actual military actions."},{"time":162000,"text":"Most are non-violent and they fall into two broad categories:"},{"time":166000,"text":"active engagement with ethnic rivalries and religious beliefs"},{"time":169000,"text":"and fair, transparent economic development"},{"time":171000,"text":"and provisioning of services."},{"time":173000,"text":"I don't know about this, but this is what I can decipher from this diagram"},{"time":176000,"text":"in 24 seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178000,"text":"When you see a diagram like this, I don't want you to be afraid."},{"time":180000,"text":"I want you to be excited. I want you to be relieved."},{"time":183000,"text":"Because simple answers may emerge."},{"time":185000,"text":"We're discovering in nature that simplicity often lies"},{"time":187000,"text":"on the other side of complexity."},{"time":189000,"text":"So for any problem, the more you can zoom out and embrace complexity,"},{"time":192000,"text":"the better chance you have of zooming in"},{"time":194000,"text":"on the simple details that matter most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}